snippet.textDisplay: This doesn't look comfortable at all. The PS controller is one of the main reasons I play PS vs Xbox. I think Sony has had most of the greatest controllers of all time. If this controller feels like shit I will certainly be pissed. Why mess with something that everyone has agreed is already pretty great. I hated the PS3 so much that I played Xbox 360s that gave me a red ring every 3 months on about 8 different consoles. This is the biggest move they have had to make and I have decided if they fuck anything up like the PS3 then I'm out on consoles for good even though I have no desire to play on mouse and keyboard.
